		"description": "<p>You are not content to leave the world as it is. You will reshape it, and you have the wherewithal to do so. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Your Strength, Dexterity, or Charisma score increases by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>When you deal radiant damage with @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.4727pnvz5nwn3h23]{Sneak Attack}, the sneak attack dice increase in size by one step and the target must make a Constitution saving throw against your maneuver DC or be Dazzled until the end of its next turn.</li>\n<li>You can use @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.my42mip0qc35rcp2]{Lay on Hands} as a bonus action</li>\n<li>You have an expertise die on saving throws against spells of the <em>illusion </em>school and on Insight checks.</li>\n</ul>",
